title: Azure VPN Gateway: BGP Settings
agents: azure
catalog: cloud/azure
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check reports the BGP settings of an Azure Virtual Network Gateway:
 the ASN, the BGP peering address, the peer weight and the number of
 configured tunnels (BGP peering addresses).

 The details of the individual tunnels are reported by the dedicated
 "Azure VPN Gateway BGP Tunnel" services, one per tunnel. The service is
 always {OK}.

item:
 The gateway name followed by "_bgp", for example "mygateway_bgp".

discovery:
 One service is created for each gateway that has BGP settings.
